---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About - Domain Discoverer" description="Discover valuable domain names faster. We provide availability checks, curated tools, and practical guides for investors, businesses, SaaS, SEO experts, and startups.">
  <section class="container-pad">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">About Domain Discoverer</h1>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">DomainDiscoverer.com helps visitors discover valuable domain names. We focus on speed, clarity, and practical workflows. Our content and tools are designed for domain investors and anyone who needs a strong name: business owners, SaaS teams, SEO experts, and startups.</p>

    <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="card p-5">
        <h2 class="font-bold mb-2">What We Do</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-white/80 space-y-1">
          <li>Instant checks to confirm domain availability</li>
          <li>Guides that explain how to evaluate names</li>
          <li>Curated tools that speed up research</li>
          <li>Practical examples that you can follow</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-5">
        <h2 class="font-bold mb-2">How We Choose Tools</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-white/80 space-y-1">
          <li>Usefulness for finding and evaluating names</li>
          <li>Transparency of pricing and data sources</li>
          <li>Track record within the domaining community</li>
          <li>Overall value for beginners and experts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-bold mb-2">Professional Standards</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80">We do not sell personal data. We only send email to people who ask to receive it. Every message includes an unsubscribe link or clear directions to opt out. We keep a simple approach to cookies and only use what is needed for the site to work.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-bold mb-2">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80">Questions or feedback are welcome. Please reach out via our <a class="underline" href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

